Paper: 9611044
Title: Black Hole Entropy in the Chern-Simons Formulation of 2+1 Gravity
Authors: Maximo Banados and Andres Gomberoff
Abstract: We examine Carlip's derivation of the 2+1 Minkowskian black hole entropy. A simplified derivation of the boundary action -valid for any value of the level k- is given.
